{"tid":1032410,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"〈醉〉原：〈龍舌蘭〉","createTime":"2019-02-22T10:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T10:54:41.000Z","uid":234351,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9975ab94760020d3414100449e084d12d318699","tid":1032410,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"見唔少人都有改〈龍舌蘭〉我又趁下墟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首曲好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係唔寫由自可一寫弊傢伙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲音難填到對不起<br />\n各位細力啲屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原曲：〈龍舌蘭〉<br />\n原詞：陳詠謙<br />\n作曲：Chris Polanco<br />\n編曲：the duo band<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n〈醉〉<br />\n改詞：可魚<br />\n<br />\n無力進退 床畔紛擾衣衫失據 有誰在顧慮<br />\n又索取 簾下光景依稀瑣碎 有誰在畏懼<br />\n身心敞開都應許 你引誘添杯再進睡<br />\n<br />\n我 逃離現實探秘<br />\n孤身天邊夜夜行 尋避世福地<br />\n深深細看陌路人 臨夜做對知己 <br />\n指尖輕撫杯邊印 缺憾美<br />\n<br />\n凌亂髮堆 難捺這身軀<br />\n這一醉 眼神在作祟<br />\n一杯酒傾乾再舉 我應約天黑了再敘<br />\n<br />\n我 逃離現實探秘<br />\n孤身天邊夜夜行 尋避世福地<br />\n深深細看陌路人 臨夜做對知己 <br />\n指尖輕撫杯邊印<br />\n想嘴裏吐香快活懷內就作戲<br />\n當天一光 醒轉說再會別揭秘<br />\n<br />\n我 無緣奉送凄美<br />\n一息呼吸撥亂紋 逢惑世鬼魅<br />\n交織剎那沒烙痕 無謂見證生死<br />\n指尖輕撫掌心印 印著妳<br />\n再添一杯美妙 細味"},{"pid":"1a1e3f4ef86d22a7a10274f838a6fe49b8e66ab0","tid":1032410,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"淫淫地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4feaab0ef66fdc5db22063482c67bcce95ff1a","tid":1032410,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"近排好多人改龍舌蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6641b3d2172b84888c8297d1d479b231ae10b1bb","tid":1032410,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{